snippet.title: No Players Online - EYE.EXE
snippet.description:
Update 1:
video of using the code found in eye.exe in No Players Online:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ShuJTUnNjU
Soul Ending: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iIGk9iuVM5I
--
New update blog post:
https://papercookies.itch.io/no-playe...

--

If you email john.mullard@yahoo.com you get an autoresponse back as follows:
"Due to personal grievances I am out of office from 03-31-1975 to 06-02-1975.

Regards,
John Mullard
Lead Networking Engineer
ENUIT LTD 
http://enuitltdgames.com/

Personal website:
http://johnmullard.itch.io/"

-

This gives you "eye.exe" that I am playing in this video.

--

the song playing is  song Kay Starr: Blue and Sentimental
The on screen lyrics are missing the word "haunt" 

If you then type "haunt" in the server select screen of No Players Online, you get a secret sound test screen. see below video.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ShuJTUnNjU

--
Also to note:
The date of the video is 03/20/1975
The auto-reply email states he will be out of office from
03-31-1975 to 06-02-1975
the video shown in eye.exe is 11 days before that, and likely when his wife died?
